Priscilla Ekwere Eleje bụ onye ntụzi izizi maka ọrụ ego na Central Bank of Nigeria (CBN)
Ọ bụkwa nwanyị izizi nke tinyere akara ya n' akwụkwọ ego nke Naijirịa, akwụkwọ ego naira
Eleje bụ nwaafọ Afikpo dị na Ebonyi State
O nwetara akara mmụta banyere akparamaagwa na Mahadum Jos, Plateau State
Humphrey Fellowship na Banking and Management na Mahadum Boston, Massachusetts, USA
Ọzọkwa, ọ bụ onye nyocha akwụkwọ (CISA)
A họpụtara Eleje ka ọ bụrụ onye ntụzi aka n' ọrụ nke Currency Operations nke ụlọ akụ apex nke Nigeria, CBN, na August 2018
Tupu oru ya, enyere ya onye nledo anya ọkwa a
Otu ego naira mbụ gosipụtara mbinye aka ya bụ akara 1000 nke batara na ntuli aka na 2019
Otu nzukọ ụmụ nwanyị nọ na Nigeria nwere obi ụtọ maka oge ọhụụ ya, ọkachasị National Council of Women Societies (NCWS), Nigeria
